page.enlisting:
• NIIX is a free service that acts as a centralized clearinghouse for
• NIIX is a free service that acts as a centralized clearinghouse for interoperable communications-related information. Interoperability planning committee members can access peer-created documents and share information with each other. NIIX represents a collaborative effort of local, tribal, state, and regional organizations to share statewide plans, agreements, policy documents and other related information through a web-based, secure location.
